{"tid":1633310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"仆街TVB，隱瞞的士撞人，只講司機被私了，share 真相俾老豆老母知","createTime":"2019-10-07T03:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T18:17:10.000Z","uid":90735,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f9e2725c7624688d5dc937b8276936867dc2feec","tid":1633310,"uid":90735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:26:16.000Z","msg":"老豆老母淨係睇TVB唔知真相，大家要share真相出去！<br />\n下面幾個Facebook專頁有講TVB幾仆街，揀一個share出去!!!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五毛電視cctvb - 廣告宣傳部</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">的士司機高速撞向人群，更令兩人危殆送院‼️<br />\nCCTVB(中央電視(乙)) 居然可以完全唔報⁉️ 仲要將個的士司機講成一名「紅衣人士」被人毆打，企圖誤導觀眾並將事發原因扭曲成「因雙方政見不同」❗️CCTVB，無恥至極點‼️🤬🤬🤬🤬🤬<br />\n【前因】的士高速撞人片段：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Itm4QH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Itm4QH&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=5abea7aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Itm4QH</a><br />\n【報導】CCTVB片段：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/338u8y4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F338u8y4&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=d8754798\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/338u8y4</a></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/72254045_467167880806733_7059600661687566336_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQkoISwKlcYU-4bflu1St-IO2lsz4tJoHundsWJ_ws3cPDjTVGIC1wm3_JaprbzAOT4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=a311d4e1c64c28f4d47199e5d96ce02d&amp;oe=5E2EF349\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F72254045_467167880806733_7059600661687566336_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQkoISwKlcYU-4bflu1St-IO2lsz4tJoHundsWJ_ws3cPDjTVGIC1wm3_JaprbzAOT4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3Da311d4e1c64c28f4d47199e5d96ce02d%26oe%3D5E2EF349&h=1bf43574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.417570699099785/467167874140067/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2Fphotos%2Fa.417570699099785%2F467167874140067%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=90b65167\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/photos/a.417570699099785/467167874140067/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>福佳與林忌創作</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果有日TVB被人放火，唔知CCTVB係咪會報導：有火焰進入了TVB錄影廠？如果有日袁志偉被人捅兩刀，唔知CCTVB係咪會報導：有廚房用具進入了袁志偉體內？<br />\n<br />\n的士瘋狂駕駛往路人撞去，最終剷上了行人路，更撞傷了幾個人，其中一位23歲女子雙腳被撞斷；偏偏CCTVB的報導，竟然只是「有的士上了行人路」，然後就報導憤怒的市民如何攻擊這位企圖謀殺的司機，這就是今日的香港，也說明了為何市民會如此憤怒</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/72203036_3368235956534842_8253952485983518720_n.png?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQmw41Ng_FFpdvKZ6FuOFgkWnfAUzE1B_PlsyCzxCXj3o85eBQlMw680zueWbrZfsiw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=395fd67d2e6bb71671cce89ff60f8808&amp;oe=5DF254C2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F72203036_3368235956534842_8253952485983518720_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQmw41Ng_FFpdvKZ6FuOFgkWnfAUzE1B_PlsyCzxCXj3o85eBQlMw680zueWbrZfsiw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D395fd67d2e6bb71671cce89ff60f8808%26oe%3D5DF254C2&h=129d2c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fokguyhk/photos/a.127094280649042/3368235953201509/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffokguyhk%2Fphotos%2Fa.127094280649042%2F3368235953201509%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=086e6388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fokguyhk/photos/a.127094280649042/3368235953201509/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>求驗傳媒</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">過了6個小時，TVB的內容沒有更新，內文繼續是「有的士上了行人路（配音及標題則有「剷上），有一名穿紅衣的男人被拖在地上圍毆」，完全沒有提及「的士衝入人群」、「女子被撞受傷」。<br />\nTVB：<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5d99c289e60383ed167b1fd1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5d99c289e60383ed167b1fd1%2F&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=a947f19a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5d99c289e60383ed167b1fd1/</a><br />\n<br />\n的士撞人片段：<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/polit&hellip;/的士疑衝上行人路撞傷途人-示威者-私了-司機至頭破血流/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolit%E2%80%A6%2F%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E7%96%91%E8%A1%9D%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%AF%E6%92%9E%E5%82%B7%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%87%B3%E9%A0%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81%2F&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=61727b5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolit%E2%80%A6%2F%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E7%96%91%E8%A1%9D%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%AF%E6%92%9E%E5%82%B7%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%87%B3%E9%A0%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81%2F&h=ce2fd316\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/polit&hellip;/的士疑衝上行人路撞傷途人-示威者-私了-司機至頭破血流/</a><br />\n（補充：TVB晚上23:36的另一條新聞，有提及「長沙灣政府合署對出有的士剷上行人路」及「警方指事後接報，指有的士撞向途人，一人受傷送院。」<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/&hellip;/5d9a0a1be603831&hellip;/藝人馬蹄露等人因拍照或政見不同起爭執被圍毆）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2F%E2%80%A6%2F5d9a0a1be603831%E2%80%A6%2F%E8%97%9D%E4%BA%BA%E9%A6%AC%E8%B9%84%E9%9C%B2%E7%AD%89%E4%BA%BA%E5%9B%A0%E6%8B%8D%E7%85%A7%E6%88%96%E6%94%BF%E8%A6%8B%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E8%B5%B7%E7%88%AD%E5%9F%B7%E8%A2%AB%E5%9C%8D%E6%AF%86%EF%BC%89&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=3224545c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/&hellip;/5d9a0a1be603831&hellip;/藝人馬蹄露等人因拍照或政見不同起爭執被圍毆）</a></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kauyim/posts/2416935291716005\" da