80zueWbrZfsiw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=395fd67d2e6bb71671cce89ff60f8808&amp;oe=5DF254C2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F72203036_3368235956534842_8253952485983518720_n.png%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQmw41Ng_FFpdvKZ6FuOFgkWnfAUzE1B_PlsyCzxCXj3o85eBQlMw680zueWbrZfsiw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3D395fd67d2e6bb71671cce89ff60f8808%26oe%3D5DF254C2&h=129d2c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fokguyhk/photos/a.127094280649042/3368235953201509/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffokguyhk%2Fphotos%2Fa.127094280649042%2F3368235953201509%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=086e6388\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fokguyhk/photos/a.127094280649042/3368235953201509/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>求驗傳媒</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">過了6個小時，TVB的內容沒有更新，內文繼續是「有的士上了行人路（配音及標題則有「剷上），有一名穿紅衣的男人被拖在地上圍毆」，完全沒有提及「的士衝入人群」、「女子被撞受傷」。<br />\nTVB：<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5d99c289e60383ed167b1fd1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5d99c289e60383ed167b1fd1%2F&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=a947f19a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5d99c289e60383ed167b1fd1/</a><br />\n<br />\n的士撞人片段：<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/polit&hellip;/的士疑衝上行人路撞傷途人-示威者-私了-司機至頭破血流/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolit%E2%80%A6%2F%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E7%96%91%E8%A1%9D%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%B7%AF%E6%92%9E%E5%82%B7%E9%80%94%E4%BA%BA-%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%86-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E8%87%B3%E9%A0%AD%E7%A0%B4%E8%A1%80%E6%B5%81%2F&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4qC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=61727b5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http